Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束 勝者八廣 2：0
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs23}game set and match 來自草地網球用語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了蘭前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用我的毛巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先都排成一列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天按照AIUEO順序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs23}あいうえお順: 沒有順序的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 排隊排隊

Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}關於強化集訓

Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這次的一年級成員怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神  很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 七惠你也稍微阻止一下她們啊  每次都那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被後輩們喜歡的帥氣的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真薄情寡義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告訴你一個好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去交個男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惠你壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我忍不住想欺負你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很壞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  和父親兩人生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但住這一整幢屋子是不是太大了點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是很令人在意嗎  這麼厚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個裡面滿滿的寫了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規定是不可以告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣  文伽你真是什麼都保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是福音局定下的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  上次那個男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋頂上追過來的那個戴著眼鏡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你還是人類的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊  美川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要向你父親開槍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什麼原因的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從那以後 一直都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0913
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0913
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  吶  那個男生是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很拚命的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是文伽的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我們不都是合同認證過的關係了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得搭檔應該是相互信賴的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送信人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個是死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從死後的世界寄來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稱為死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後的 世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立石尚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是寄信人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這也是理所應當的反應啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說  那算什麼啊  真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是死了的話  才不幫你送死後文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朝  給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的臉  發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  蘭前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來一起玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩紙牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我收斂點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會影響到其他的客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又有什麼關係呢  隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是蘭前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真通情達理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過相對的 輸掉的人要場地快跑10個來回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼辦文伽  他們都出了海鷗市了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 申請出差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 好久沒去管轄區外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去外邊咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡很討厭這個城市麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是再喜歡的食物 每天都吃的話也會厭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公  你這麼慢吞吞的沒關係麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察不忙說明社會安定嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到美川了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那起事件的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 七惠今年晉陞到隊長了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  也請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的都寫在這上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  5點左右送過來可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個我要去倉庫看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  多買點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事叫的這麼性感幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟男生交往的女人很噁心麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是討厭男生呢  蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是和爸爸一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不算異性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡作劇的話是不是太纏人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這不是惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是立石尚子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄我的不是她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為我沒有接受的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有送到的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我是不會收的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  完全被討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這是死人發出來的信 都會讓人感到害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封死後文能送到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真想得開啊  年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是千秋 為什麼你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出差到這裡了 真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0923
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一陣子剛在上面見過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  這裡是千秋的投遞範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  我說……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認投遞範圍是搭檔的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健忘這點倒很像個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  你個番茄汁 給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是番茄  是真苫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你這張破嘴巴該換一張了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  你們的相聲可以停了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面確實經常見到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上是好久不見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強詞奪理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  強詞奪理強詞奪理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後文的投遞人是死人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說年齡本應不會增長的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻不同  年齡在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次見你  你都長大了些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人

Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  全壘打 總共三個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事麼  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  青砥你太得意忘形了點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  再來一球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱先遣隊 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  那個叫立石尚子的 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不是說她很早以前就去世了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是跟男人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是10多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很恨她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以當我聽說她是被男人給騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後變得落魄的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為那是她活該
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然都追到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是你媽媽寄來的信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是她女兒吧  好歹也看下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的信 我要怎樣是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣同意了啊  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣是對死後文的褻瀆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對死人表達敬意的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡 我們的工作只是將死後文送達而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後是收信人的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  加油  加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  加油  加油……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 加油……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚去趟醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師會來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就讓他們開車送你到山下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了就來了 不過也沒什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因就是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說對不起是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 雖然這不是我該說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是扔掉了 你也只會比以前更在意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直守在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惠你真壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:16:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊  隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}五  六
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會想去救人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們送信人是規定不可以做直接跟人類的性命相關的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音局定下的十四條大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是違反了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  因為文伽很負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想去確認下死後文是否真的有送到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  是這樣的吧  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 想要看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  已經聯絡過消防隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  拜託你了老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 老師怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青砥 接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
