Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這個不是道歉就能夠彌補的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我這樣的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭還是很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的正式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭到最後都沒有氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一年的比賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好的回敬他們了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭從以前就不服輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高中校際比賽的半決賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是司線員的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的發球肯定沒出界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級的團體賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家輸掉的比分全部贏回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連練習比賽都來看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還一場場都寫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧你看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭的媽媽  是一個怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視人們各種各樣的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徑直奔跑著的你所追求的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了

